Path: This week in Nu #52
Content:
One year of TwiN!
samhedin changed per-directory environments to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2352] run exit scripts in the original directory
JosephTLyons updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2354] ``histogram``
 occurrences examples
, added a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2358] test for 
``count``
, fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2374] column count breaking on empty tables
mattclarke renamed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2356] time units (eg 
``1s``
 is now 
``1sec``
)
jonathandturner changed 
``to json``
 to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2359] preserve metadata in output
, moved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2369] nu-cli data functionality into its own crate, nu-data
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2372] testing wasm to CI
lucasmmg changed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2360] ``sort-by``
 to fail gracefully when types are mismatched
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2366] further improved the error
rrichardson added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2363] new case conversions to 
``str``
andrasio cleaned up 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2364] config settings logic
fdncred added support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2365] more Nu table themes
, and more 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2378] table theming
bailey-layzer added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2377] type inference for alias definitions
LhKipp added a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2381] ``sleep``
 command
, fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/book/pull/125] time units in the book
jzaefferer improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/demo/pull/59] tracking errors on the demo site
, and updated the demo to the latest Nu
oylenshpeegal fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/contributor-book/pull/28] typo in the contributor book
